Introduction

Bling Bling was a South Korean girl group under MAJOR9. They debuted on both Korea and Japan in November 17, 2020 with the digital single "G.G.B".

On July 26, 2022, MAJOR9 announced Bling Bling's disbandment after almost two years of promotions.
